{"tid":298980,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"(遊記)兩gay佬毒遊大阪京都奈良","createTime":"2017-06-26T16:43:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-15T05:51:19.000Z","uid":5190,"like":18,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8192f46a784eefa33e35e1bb3740da726525eba5","tid":298980,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T16:43:40.000Z","msg":"小弟今次第一次寫遊記 如果真係悶 唔好睇都請你唔好負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我依家依個時間已經係尾二個日 聽日就要飛返香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以 應該會有更新<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實成個去大阪嘅目的係為左去潮聖K-ON係套動漫 有睇過嘅朋友都應該知到有間學校 而去依間學校係我依次旅行嘅其中一個目的地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n總共係去左6日 有兩日都係得半日 好可惜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我地貪平機票坐HKexpress 1135起飛 順利1645降落日本關西<br />\n第一次黎到日本 睇啲路線圖睇到頭都大撚埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/27/003503_2f541d135b39823a5a63ef0e88d892c4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F27%2F003503_2f541d135b39823a5a63ef0e88d892c4.jpg&h=59781449&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地依次日本旅行係全程用icoca 除左去學校個到 因為太鄉下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n幾經辛苦 順利了解左點搭後 就即刻離開機場 去左我fd子想去嘅 outlet<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/27/003757_fa1a0e726f092d4e8e9e4859342aa943.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F27%2F003757_fa1a0e726f092d4e8e9e4859342aa943.jpg&h=0f5d0c3c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n係outlet出面仲見到個好靚嘅日落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/27/003807_964e22e7bef2607c6953c012f22f6416.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F27%2F003807_964e22e7bef2607c6953c012f22f6416.jpg&h=090f76b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n個種因為日本啲樓好矮而望到一大片天空 一望無際嘅感覺真係好爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n行完outlet之後就搭車去我地嘅民宿地點 位於日本橋附近 近黑門市場<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/27/004317_4fb6c0ab9f13af6f88b8dc06d1b35358.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F27%2F004317_4fb6c0ab9f13af6f88b8dc06d1b35358.jpg&h=b4fc26e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n 所以第二朝我地好早起身去左黑門市場食野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"976e43aecbd15c77a04e837d0d06ef189d60aed6","tid":298980,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T16:46:22.000Z","msg":"好眼瞓 食家日本差唔多兩點 聽朝再打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n希望有人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e1f7552f4746a2d79f7e21ddc0ed1e6b1a10c56","tid":298980,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T16:46:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好眼瞓 依家日本差唔多兩點 聽朝再打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n希望有人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"87b18e350ab8718e766847b109c8fd2864e87fa9","tid":298980,"uid":53413,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T16:47:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e44711dbb3feef379e52ff439761c578f9b47d63","tid":298980,"uid":875,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T16:47:44.000Z","msg":"推 遲啲都去<br />\n巴打你6日預咗幾錢？"},{"pid":"1d18d16365aa1c82acd0cc395795223a97c35c09","tid":298980,"uid":62653,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T16:47:52.000Z","msg":"會唔會去叫雞？"},{"pid":"b7cc5f59df860d5bafea5cee91044fd85454df47","tid":298980,"uid":33727,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T16:50:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>會唔會去叫雞？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\ngay佬去叫雞 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9aa56858c034e1ecdd6be653c1490706ec0c3d39","tid":298980,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T16:52:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>會唔會去叫雞？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\ngay佬去叫雞 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n友情之間嘅稱呼姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05bd46857a29134c2e8696a75d1856e6b74cceef","tid":298980,"uid":5190,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T16:53:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>推 遲啲都去<br />\n巴打你6日預咗幾錢？</blockquote><br />\n帶左8萬円 無買太多野 多數食"},{"pid":"e73a2f60e04dafb0e4fcb47393b452bd6b876c9b","tid":298980,"uid":34147,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T16:54:44.000Z","msg":"你個部咩相機嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bb29c1703e98d7933888db283c67401b729fd65","tid":298980,"uid":875,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T16:57:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>推 遲啲都去<br />\n巴打你6日預咗幾錢？</blockquote><br />\n帶左8萬円 無買太多野 多數食</blockquote><br />\n睇吓你洗成點先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 要參考吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24eb2f07d63d0ec0849279788d1f92182da6b438","tid":298980,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T03:08:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你個部咩相機嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\niPhone 5s<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f6266645834fb6493ea06aba502a80c3fd49982","tid":298980,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T03:08:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你個部咩相機嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\niPhone se<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"436a159fee7fae97a12c4ef71192ae297b21a26a","tid":298980,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T03:52:25.000Z","msg":"終於起身 可以繼續打了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nDay 2 我地留係大阪 去左黑門市場 難波 道頓堀 心齋橋 美國村<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為我地住得近黑門市場 所以一朝早8點起身就去左黑門市場食最新鮮嘅野食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n第一次黎黑門市場 嗅到陣海水味真係無得頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n無論黑毛和牛 神户牛 壽司剌身應有盡有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲有好多熟食 香噴噴嘅牛油燒帶子 串燒牛柳粒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/27/112021_3e225af688cd7c8ea9b326a891ed258d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F27%2F112021_3e225af688cd7c8ea9b326a891ed258d.jpg&h=1293741a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/27/112029_a1bdafef8f3dfca0231c665f1721475e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F27%2F112029_a1bdafef8f3dfca0231c665f1721475e.jpg&h=555428fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n影得太少 因為掛住食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n食完就去搭車去難波 去到難波 全程靠Google map 因為事前少準備<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過Google 大神真係好好用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n由於難波 心齋橋 道頓堀 美國村三個地方都好近 撞撞下就會行左去第二條街 所以我地見路就行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/27/112546_625a671cd825061bde928753c1669c62.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F27%2F112546_625a671cd825061bde928753c1669c62.jpg&h=080c6d5b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/27/112611_15f99e1941bd47ab7e861738d615b2a6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F27%2F112611_15f99e1941bd47ab7e861738d615b2a6.jpg&h=fd6aad42&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/27/112714_ebf03715c2e782e8ec0831ff2df78930.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F27%2F112714_ebf03715c2e782e8ec0831ff2df78930.jpg&h=0e6a07be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n係超級多人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 心齋橋同女人街好似 好多賣衫賣鞋 都有好多賣野食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我地午餐都係係心齋橋食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n西餐<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/27/114145_c93d8dba6b5b7f032f0dc7a7a91b3261.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F27%2F114145_c93d8dba6b5b7f032f0dc7a7a91b3261.jpg&h=864ea9e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n依一日全日都係行街同行街 所以都影唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n夜晚就去左民宿附近一間叫做 <span style=\"color: red;\">餃子王將</span>嘅拉麵店食野 啲餸都比較中式 有炒飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 啲廚師都係帶點心帽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/27/115201_30ba7ae12b54674a5d5da400b1d9d149.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F27%2F115201_30ba7ae12b54674a5d5da400b1d9d149.jpg&h=4546b1ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大阪嘅一日就係咁 完左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a01190ed89369cd7dc4c65c8ad4d61a5a58ba656","tid":298980,"uid":64889,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T03:55:29.000Z","msg":"留個名先"},{"pid":"62ec7aa7ca95d81d76c82777a4c074c1aff4d841","tid":298980,"uid":90166,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T03:59:58.000Z","msg":"巴打都係食野多"},{"pid":"445801029cfe0da91c6bf4b0a42aff419d98c68d","tid":298980,"uid":5190,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T04:02:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打都係食野多</blockquote><br />\n因為個人唔太shopping 黎到以食為主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"032eb67928d8406a756bd098de2de70d557130e3","tid":298980,"uid":90166,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T04:05:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>巴打都係食野多</blockquote><br />\n因為個人唔太shopping 黎到以食為主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都係<br />\n映多d美食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fff0b8bac07b90ae440b5554203f8a40368c1479","tid":298980,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T04:07:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>巴打都係食野多</blockquote><br />\n因為個人唔太shopping 黎到以食為主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都係<br />\n映多d美食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n今日飛啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30c62276aef327012d6a145f604eb46ed3a6d629","tid":298980,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T04:39:28.000Z","msg":"Day3 就係要前往我嘅豐鄉小學嘅日子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個種朝聖嘅感覺真係好緊張<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依一日仲要更加早起身 7點就醒左 因為去個間學校係要好長時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 遠到好似返左鄉下咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n由大阪搭Jr去到京都 又係第一次搭Jr 睇到頭都痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為要早起身 所食左個飯團同密瓜包就起行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n京都站<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/27/123035_1baa701d726f100bed9edc31c961a122.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F27%2F123035_1baa701d726f100bed9edc31c961a122.jpg&h=fd3b5951&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n京都有一個好特別嘅文化 平時香港搭電梯都係左行右企 日本都唔例外 但黎到京都 竟然係左企右行 今日終於知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/27/123257_4534d7cd3cd9bda42bdc65ef9fca3347.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F27%2F123257_4534d7cd3cd9bda42bdc65ef9fca3347.jpg&h=474a54d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n坐左差唔多一粒鐘嘅時間 終於到左近江八幡 我地要係依個站轉搭電車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 而且 係幾乎半個鐘先有一班<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/27/123517_e840e1ced1f328245e00cb68bf7d53bd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F27%2F123517_e840e1ced1f328245e00cb68bf7d53bd.jpg&h=a2559283&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n搭電車嘅途中 都見到有幾個日本學生 日本鄉下妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 發覺日本嘅鄉下妹好多都係剪冬菇頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 見到有個幾靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但我無影到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n去到八日市 又係時候轉車 所以去左轉廁所 又發現一樣幾搞笑嘅野貼係女廁門口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/27/123819_706912e3d441236ea86dbd033eecbe3f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F27%2F123819_706912e3d441236ea86dbd033eecbe3f.jpg&h=42fb31ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n連登仔 唔好偷拍呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n打到依到先 等等打埋下半篇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44b8b99faef4f1b7e8b84b571ca4a261bdb50de2","tid":298980,"uid":90166,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T05:15:16.000Z","msg":"其實日本係右企左行<br />\n得大阪唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d08ab0cd3c10cd360501fbe130b9dcc4c4f9ca03","tid":298980,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T05:21:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實日本係右企左行<br />\n得大阪唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但係京都係左企右行 其他都係左行右企<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d602a8b6a9ed8178558c553cb2dc6253c4df1de2","tid":298980,"uid":90166,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T05:27:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實日本係右企左行<br />\n得大阪唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但係京都係左企右行 其他都係左行右企<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我分錯左左右<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n得大阪同香港一樣右企左行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d6d4615f88ccde46a6bb02f5c0e51111c865a55","tid":298980,"uid":5190,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T07:11:36.000Z","msg":"下半篇<br />\n<br />\n係火車上面震左幾個字就到豐鄉了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/27/145017_63aeaa48f799bc4341c2511d5b256a6c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F27%2F145017_63aeaa48f799bc4341c2511d5b256a6c.jpg&h=db114b7d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n由於豐鄉因為K-ON依套動漫而多左人黎觀光 所以當地周圍都有好多關於K-ON嘅物品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/27/145225_46e21cb5ca385ae3ca454b91db5dbaae.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F27%2F145225_46e21cb5ca385ae3ca454b91db5dbaae.jpg&h=1c0cc84e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/27/145243_fff0129b9d4e47d9d69a337957df5aca.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F27%2F145243_fff0129b9d4e47d9d69a337957df5aca.jpg&h=82adb5fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/27/145258_f531d459e437d5881c4660ac7b4c10f9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F27%2F145258_f531d459e437d5881c4660ac7b4c10f9.jpg&h=a6dc9a70&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/27/145321_519555a435734141d21995d2ac465ad5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F27%2F145321_519555a435734141d21995d2ac465ad5.jpg&h=93ab3612&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/27/145333_f93a90f1bdca95bece5530c19a1f066d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F27%2F145333_f93a90f1bdca95bece5530c19a1f066d.jpg&h=c1678865&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n間學校都好近車站 所以好快就行到 第一眼見到學校 不禁比個讚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/27/145625_8ded78401b553d548602f774f74c080e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F27%2F145625_8ded78401b553d548602f774f74c080e.jpg&h=e1943187&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/27/145636_8b250efb51d08b9b5ac0a1f30a8bba69.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F27%2F145636_8b250efb51d08b9b5ac0a1f30a8bba69.jpg&h=c49d187f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n依間學校由以前小學到依家成為左當地居民嘅圖書館 入到去嘅感覺就係<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">好感動呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/27/145839_713d2b0b011b85719da97bacfa18841d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F27%2F145839_713d2b0b011b85719da97bacfa18841d.jpg&h=4ef86ec1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/27/145851_ff2fe1734104360558b8331120460e8e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F27%2F145851_ff2fe1734104360558b8331120460e8e.jpg&h=60f5fb82&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/27/145901_62417f4cce928989284ec7cf98ca73eb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F27%2F145901_62417f4cce928989284ec7cf98ca73eb.jpg&h=f9902473&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/27/145912_e55671c16eaa107c2be5b4ae0b1c8796.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F27%2F145912_e55671c16eaa107c2be5b4ae0b1c8796.jpg&h=830b5ed5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n親身黎到依間學校 作為fans嘅我 終於完左個心願<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/27/150638_1dfc3f52b670bb2162f3e6ec9e215929.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F27%2F150638_1dfc3f52b670bb2162f3e6ec9e215929.jpg&h=770cbb9e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/27/150654_0f54f3dbd46cd5fee0918e437f2a57a1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F27%2F150654_0f54f3dbd46cd5fee0918e437f2a57a1.jpg&h=dff1d99e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/27/150707_fa3024dff84d44e94665b87c78cfc602.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F27%2F150707_fa3024dff84d44e94665b87c78cfc602.jpg&h=b7fc2a1a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/27/150721_4fd56c583a505ecc81c4cf50150b387a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F27%2F150721_4fd56c583a505ecc81c4cf50150b387a.jpg&h=0621b3f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n到我地走個時 原本諗住係個到食埋野先走 點知因為星期六所以無開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後唯有返京都搵野食 就咁樣 去一轉豐鄉用左全日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n去到京都都仲未天黑<br />\n<br />\n京都塔<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/27/150936_452361cae7fba9f2b8d09758a364c74a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F27%2F150936_452361cae7fba9f2b8d09758a364c74a.jpg&h=8d947584&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n係京都站個商場搵左間蛋包飯餐廳食野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n都幾好味<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/27/151108_94c101d1f63015ee19a1c3f9440f1c5d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F27%2F151108_94c101d1f63015ee19a1c3f9440f1c5d.jpg&h=90ac2ba8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n食完就順順利利返左民宿了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fe51222949d5f1bbb2b71d64b95e42941213b88","tid":298980,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T07:12:18.000Z","msg":"上機了 唔打住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}